name: Birch Tree Ring
description:
Birch Tree Ring
2010
sterling silver, model railroad landscape materials
3.5” x 2” x 2”
one-of-a-kind

A fantastical landscape atop your finger!

A lone birch tree perches on a handformed sterling silver "hill" complete with rocks and bushes.  The underside of the dome is roller-printed with the texture of a real leaf, and the ring shank is cast from a real dogwood branch.  

The ring comes with a handmade cherry wood stand to display your piece when you are not wearing it at the next garden party.

name: Culvert
description:
Culvert
2010
sterling silver, 14k yellow gold, prehnite, model railroad landscape materials
8” x 5” x .5”

A branch split lengthwise down the middle and cast in sterling silver provides the horizon line for this small landscape necklace.  A sterling silver tree sprouts pear-shaped prehnite in the palest of green set in 14k yellow gold prong settings.  Underneath, a lone sterling root makes its way underground with determination.  Peer into the plaster model railroad culvert next to the tree--there's no telling where we are headed.

Sterling silver cable and clasp.  Necklace falls at around 18".

name: Field Necklace
description:
Field Necklace
2010
sterling silver, brass plated chain, model railroad field grass, pearl
chain length: 30”

A formal field study.

A circle of anemone buds is at the heart of this swinging necklace, hanging from sterling silver chain and linked with a length of brass-plated chain.  Two brooms of model railroad field grass hang along one side of a longer chain, and a black pearl capped with a sterling silver acorn cap cast from the real thing swings below.

name: Small Branch Necklace
description:
Small Branch Necklace
2010
sterling silver, 14k yellow gold, prehnite, pearl, model railroad landscape materials
13” x 2.5” x .5”

A small horizontal branch holds a tiny world to marvel at.  Two sterling silver anemone buds huddle together while a pear-shaped rose cut prehnite in a 14k yellow gold setting sprouts from the other side of the sterling branch.  Below, a black pearl set in a sterling acorn cap hangs at a distance.

Two small lengths of sterling cable chain on one side complement the larger chain on the other.  The necklace falls at around 18".

name: Trunkscape
description:
Trunkscape
2008
sterling silver, model railroad tree stands, cubic zirconia
approx. 12” x 8” x .5”
one-of-a-kind

A fantasy landscape of cast-off tree trunk bases from model railroad trees--some plastic, some cast in silver.  

Round, brilliant cut cubic zirconia is flush into the larger sterling tree bases, and silver rivets complete the smaller bases.  The chain is constructed from rings cut from the bases, and the necklace clasp is hidden under a final trunk base at the neck.  

Green silk thread ties the trunk bases together, and allows lots of movement and play.

name: Landscape Sample Necklace
description:
Landscape Sample Necklace
2008
sterling silver, model landscape materials
approx. 12” x 6” x .75”
one-of-a-kind

My investigation reveals that there are several landscape materials that deserve closer examination.  With this necklace you can get up close with five of them--"talus," "yellow field grass," "bush," cast sterling silver lily buds, and "green field grass."  

The miniature model railroad landscape materials provide a confounding contrast to the full-scale cast sterling silver natural forms--the lily buds, the branch that the vials hang from, and the chain, which is made up of small sections of another branch.

The necklace falls at around 18" and closes with a toggle clasp.

name: Bush and Branch Double Pendant
description:
Bush/Branch Double Pendant
2007
sterling silver, model railroad “bush”
18” cable length
one-of-a-kind

This seemingly simple necklace marries large and small, natural and artificial, real and illusory.

A miniature model railroad bush mounted on a sterling dome sidles up next to a full scale branch cast from the real thing.  

Which is real and which is fabrication?

Sterling silver cable chain measures 18" in length.

name: Grass Necklace
description:
Grass Necklace
2007
sterling silver, model railroad “field grass”
necklace: 5.5” inside diameter
one-of-a-kind

Five tufts of green model railroad field grass are spotlighted in sterling settings and strung along sterling cable.  The whole necklace is oxidized and then given a brushed finish to bring out the luster of the silver beneath.

Necklace hangs at around 18".

name: Bush/Branch Necklace
description:
Bush/Branch Necklace
2007
sterling silver, model railroad “bushes” and “underbrush”
necklace: 6.25” inside diameter
one-of-a-kind

Model railroad bushes in two shade of green mounted on sterling silver alternate with full scale sterling branches cast from the real thing.  

Sterling silver cable with handmade toggle clasp.  Necklace falls at around 19".

name: Winter Tree Pendant
description:
Winter Tree Pendant
2007
sterling silver, plastic model railroad tree armature
18” cable length

A simple statement piece.  One plastic model railroad tree armature free of foliage and adornment hangs from a sterling setting and a sterling cable.  The whole piece is oxidized and then given a light brushed finish. 

Cable--18".

name: Landscape Sample Rings (under glass)
description:
Landscape Sample rings (under glass)
2007
sterling silver, glass, model railroad landscape materials
each approx. 2.5” x 1" x .5”
one-of-a-kind

Landscape specimens under glass for wear or display.

Each ring showcases an individual model railroad landscape material--"bush," "field grass," "talus."  Each specimen is enclosed firmly under lab glass like a scientific curio, ready for your experiments or examination.

Sterling silver bezels and shanks.

The three rings come with a gorgeous handmade stand made of cherry wood so that you can display the rings on a shelf or table when you are not wearing or examining them.

name: Tree Pendants on Chain
description:
Tree Pendant on Chain
2007
sterling silver, 24k
pendant: 2” x 2” x .5” 
chain length: 18”

These cast sterling silver tree pendants drip with 24k yellow gold leaves. 

Each pendant can be ordered in natural silver or oxidized silver, and hangs from a sterling silver cable chain.

name: Silver Tree Pendant with 24k and Aquamarine
description:
Tree Pendant with
Aquamarine and 24k
2007
sterling silver, 24k, aquamarine
pendant: 2” x 2” x .5”
cable length: 18”

This cast sterling silver tree pendant features a natural, faceted chunk of aquamarine and tiny handformed 24k gold leaves.

name: Large Tree Brooch
description:
Large Tree Brooch
2007
sterling silver, 24k
2.5” x 2.5” x .5”

A sterling silver tree drips with rich 24k gold leaves.  The perfect tree for any season.  Two tie tack pin backs keep the brooch wherever you want it--perfect for a jacket or suit.

name: Silver Tree Earrings
description:
Tree Earrings
2007
sterling silver
2.5” x 2” x .5”

Cast sterling silver trees suspended from sterling silver ear wires grow boldly from your ears.

name: Silver Branch Earrings
description:
Silver Branch Earrings
2007
sterling silver

Branch earrings in sterling silver with a subtle brushed surface.

Sterling silver post backs.

small: 1.25" x .75”
medium: 1.75” x 1.25”
large: 2” x 1.5” 

These earrings are also available in an oxidized version with 24k gold leaves.  Please see my other listings to view this option.

name: Oxidized Branch Earrings with Gold Leaf
description:
Oxidized Silver Branch Earrings
2007
sterling silver, 24k

A take on my branch earrings--oxidized to a rich black and then brushed for subtle texture.  One perfect handformed 24k gold leaf completes each earring.  

Sterling silver post backs.

small: 1.25” x .75” 
medium: 1.75” x 1.25” 
large: 2” x 1.5” 

These earrings are also available in a natural silver color.  Please see my other listings in my Big Cartel shop to view this version.

name: Malden Avenue East Rings
description:
Malden Avenue East Rings
from Structural Series #1: Decomposition
1999
sterling silver, chinese lantern pods, copper, enamel, fine silver
each approx. 1.5” x 1” x .5”

Three rings made from and inspired by chinese lantern pods found growing out of a crack in the sidewalk on Malden Avenue East on Capitol Hill in Seattle, WA.

Two rings feature natural, untreated chinese lantern pods--one fully intact and sporting the bright orange skin that these pods are known for, and one whose orange flesh has been eaten away naturally by wind and rain.  The third ring is built by hand from sterling, fine silver, copper and enamel, and kiln fired to an organic orange peel texture.

The tallest ring measures approximately 1.5" x 1" x .5"

These rings come in a handmade custom cherry wood shadow box to display the rings on a wall or a shelf.

name: Savannah Necklace
description:
Savannah Necklace
2000
sterling silver, live oak pods, silk cord
approx. 18" length
one-of-a-kind

Cast sterling silver live oak caps--both singles and doubles--from trees along the beautiful boulevards in Savannah, Georgia hold real live oak acorns.  The acorns are strung on knotted silk cord. 

This necklace is approximately 18" in length.

This necklace was featured in Seattle Magazine, Russian Jeweler Magazine, and Grazia Magazine.

name: Savannah Bracelet
description:
Savannah Bracelet
2000
live oak pods, elastic
2" diameter
edition of three

Perfect specimens from live oaks along the tree-lined boulevards in Savannah, Georgia are strung on clear stretchy elastic.  Instant transport to the long, lazy days of summer in the south.

This bracelet was produced in an edition of three.

name: Sanibel Island Rings
description:
Sanibel Island Rings
2001
sterling silver, found organic materials
tallest ring approx. 2" x 1" x .5"
one-of-a-kind

This set of three rings is made from natural materials collected one summer on Sanibel Island, off the coast of Florida.  These natural specimens are highlighted perfectly and effortlessly with the clean lines of sterling silver rings.

These rings are sold in a handmade cherry wood shadow box to display the pieces on a wall or on a shelf.

One-of-a-kind.

name: Spice Pendants
description:
Single Spice Pendants
2007
sterling silver, handblown glass bottles, whole spices
pendants approx. .5" x 1" x .5"
18" chain length
available in any combination of spice/bottle shape

Handblown glass bottles contain small specimens of perfect elemental natural forms--whole spices.

Each pendant is approximately 1" x .5", depending on which shape of bottle you choose.  Pendants hang from 18" of sterling silver cable chains that close with handmade clasps.

These pendants are available in any combination of spice/bottle shape.

name: Element
description:
Element
from Structural Series #2: Deconstruction
1999
sterling silver, 18k gold
7” x 5” x .5”
one-of-a-kind

Simple, clean, elemental.

This sterling silver torque necklace capped off with 18k yellow gold balls sprouts three small, perfect 18k gold flowers.  An instant reminder of the fragility of natural forms and the inherent beauty of a simple bloom.

Necklace measures approximately 7" x 5" x .5"

One-of-a-kind.

name: Three Rings
description:
Three Rings
from Structural Series #2: Deconstruction
1999
18k gold, sterling silver
each approx. 1” x 2” x .5”
one-of-a-kind

From the Gold/Silver Series, three elemental 18k yellow gold and sterling silver rings to wear or display.  This set of three rings explores the minimum needed to suggest flower forms, the lines of the rings like gestural drawings on paper.

The tallest ring is approximately 2" x 1" x .5"

These rings come in a handmade cherry wood shadow box perfect for displaying the rings on a shelf or on a wall.

One-of-a-kind

name: Decay
description:
Decay
2001
sterling silver
7” x 7” x 1”
one-of-a-kind

A sterling silver framework supports sterling flower forms in various states of growth and decay.  This piece has a loose, gestural quality that makes it easy to wear and even somewhat moldable to your unique neckline.

One-of-a-kind

name: Delhi: Summer
description:
Delhi: Summer
2000
sterling silver, photographs of leaves
approx. 19" length
one-of-a-kind

Slices of a perfect country summer--around your neck.  

Sterling silver bezel frames in the shape of leaves hold blurry photographs of leaves and are covered in clear resin for durability.  The graceful shape of the leaves and stems is echoed in the flow of the necklace itself around your neck.

The necklace falls at around 19" and is a one-of-a-kind piece.

name: Sterling Silver Lilac Twig Ring with 18k Gold and White Diamond
description:
Sterling silver twig band cast from a beautiful lilac bush in my garden.

An 18k yellow gold tapered tube setting holds a 3mm white diamond. The smooth and modern lines of the setting contrast perfectly with the rougher, organic feel of the band.

Diamond: .10ct, 3mm, VS white brilliant cut diamond

All of my diamonds are ethically sourced, and purchased from reputable sellers who do not knowingly buy or trade in conflict diamonds.

Made to order in your size in about three weeks.

name: Sterling Silver Twig Ring with Rose Gold and Morganite
description:
An absolutely stunning faceted oval morganite weighing in at over 1 carat is showcased beautifully in a tall, tapered 14k rose gold bezel setting. The rosy color of the gold perfectly accents the pretty pink of the morganite. The setting sits atop a sterling silver twig ring cast from a real dogwood branch.

Morganite is also known as pink beryl, rose beryl, pink emerald, and cesian beryl, and is a rare light pink to rose-colored gem.

This ring would make a stunning engagement ring. See the last photo for a picture of the ring with a plain silver twig wedding band.

Morganite: 8mm x 6mm

This ring is made to order in your size in about four weeks.

name: Sterling Silver Ring with Whisky Quartz and Diamond
description:
An absolutely gorgeous 10mm whisky quartz stone sits in a handmade 18k bezel on top of a sterling silver ring cast from a real dogwood branch. Next to the whisky quartz is a diamond set in a 14k yellow gold tapered tube setting.

Diamond: 3mm, 10pt, .10 carat, white brilliant cut VS diamond

All of my diamonds are ethically sourced, and purchased from reputable sellers who do not knowingly buy or trade in conflict diamonds.

This ring is made to order in your size in about three weeks.

name: Wrapped Sterling Silver Twig Band with White Diamond
description:
Natural. Dazzling. Botanical. Brilliant.

A slim sterling silver twig cast from nature is wrapped to form the perfect petite ring. A 14k yellow gold basket setting cradles a 4mm sparkling white diamond.

Diamond: .25ct, 4mm, VS white brilliant cut diamond

All of my diamonds are ethically sourced, and purchased from reputable sellers who do not knowingly buy or trade in conflict diamonds.

Made to order in your size in about three weeks.

name: Sterling Silver Twig Ring with Tiny Diamonds
description:
A slim sterling silver lilac band cast from a section of lilac branch from my garden.

Flush set into the band are three tiny 1mm diamonds.

Perfect for an understated wedding band, paired with any of my twig engagement rings, or on its own as an everyday ring with a touch of luxe.

Diamonds: .15 tcw, VS, 1mm white diamonds

All of my diamonds are ethically sourced, and purchased from reputable sellers who do not knowingly buy or trade in conflict diamonds.

This ring is made to order in your size in about three weeks.

name: Hammered Hoop Ring with Champagne Diamond
description:
An organic, hammered sterling silver hoop encircles a gorgeous sparkling 3mm champagne diamond in a 14k yellow gold bezel.

The hammered half round band meets the edges of the hoop and provides a surprisingly comfortable fit.

Diamond: 3mm, VS, .10ct champagne

All of my diamonds are ethically sourced, and purchased from reputable sellers who do not knowingly buy or trade in conflict diamonds.

Made to Order in your size in about three weeks.

name: Sterling Twig Solitaire Ring with White Sapphire
description:
Small, delicate and perfect.

Sterling silver twig band with one small, precious AA grade 3.5mm white sapphire in a 14k yellow gold solitaire setting.

This ring is made to order in your size. Please allow three weeks for your ring to ship.
